txt.en: There is much to be done in the Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha.
Enter the enemy encampment of Dûm Boha

You notice the encampment of Dûm Boha is littered with maggot-holes. The Orcs seem to use these networks of tunnels to come and go about the Slag-hills. Perhaps sealing up the holes will limit their movement and communication.
The Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha is located on the western slopes of the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should seal off the maggot-hole entrances scattered around the encampment.
The Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha is located on the western slopes of the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should seal off the maggot-hole entrances scattered around the encampment.
You have sealed off many of the maggot-holes scattered about the hillside. This should severely limit the movement of Orcs beneath the hills.
Sealed off many of the maggot-holes in Dûm Boha.
